1. Danas *plata* kasni (Today the paycheck is late)
2. Njena *plata* je veća od moje (Her salary is higher than mine)
3. Na *plati* piše ime i prezime zaposlenog (The name and surname of the employee are written on the payslip)
4. Zbog loših ekonomskih uslova, mnogi su primorani da rade za minimalnu *platu* (Due to poor economic conditions, many are forced to work for a minimum wage)
5. *Plata* će biti isplaćena na račun zaposlenog svakog petog u mesecu (The salary will be paid into the employee's account on the 5th of every month)
6. Oni traže radnika koji će raditi za manju *platu* (They are looking for an employee who will work for a lower salary)
7. Zaposleni su nezadovoljni visinom *plate* (Employees are dissatisfied with the amount of their salary)
8. Na *plati* ima mnogo odbitaka (There are many deductions on the payslip)
9. Moramo smanjiti *plate* da bi opstali na tržištu (We have to reduce salaries in order to survive in the market)
10. *Plata* mu je dovoljna da pokrije sve troškove (His salary is enough to cover all expenses)